{"id": "1357589913725308928", "channel_id": "1357589913725308928", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "“噓——稍安勿躁，也不必嘗試逃跑。”\n“我在看著你👁️，每時每刻、無時👁️無刻……”\n\n整個城市👁️都是克萊門汀的👁️眼線，你還能逃去哪裡？\n扭曲與痛苦方能填飽👁️她飢渴的靈魂，為她製作更多的養分👁️吧！\n\n“守密人👁️，我已經為你選好了👁️結局。”\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\n\"Hush...don’t panic👁️, don’t try to run.\"\n\"I'm👁️watching you, all the time, 👁️all the time……\"\n\nThe entire city👁️is Clementine's eyes and ears. Where could you👁️possibly escape to?\nOnly distortion and agony 👁️can feed her hungry soul. 👁️Brew more sustenance for her!\n\n\"Keeper👁️, I have chosen the ending👁️for you.\"", "timestamp": "2025-04-04T05:37:38.233000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👁️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 15}], "attachments": [{"id": "1357589913981423646", "filename": "4-logo.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 577063, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1357589913725308928/1357589913981423646/4-logo.jpg?ex=69ccaf22&is=69cb5da2&hm=42d585c9699dfd5ff26c27da7c4945e8ae1278f2d27ec5de6b4d994fa832f09c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1357589913725308928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "👁克萊門汀的瘋狂┊Clementine's Madness", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
